          <i class="fas fa-fire text-red-500 text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-3">Heating Repair</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-4">Fast, reliable repair for all heating systems — furnaces, heat pumps and more — with 24/7 coverage.</p>
